235
00:20:37,422 --> 00:20:39,033
Apa maksud semua ini?

236
00:20:39,093 --> 00:20:40,762
Siapa dia, dan kenapa dia...

237
00:20:40,762 --> 00:20:43,533
Nanti kujelaskan. Nanti.

238
00:20:44,573 --> 00:20:47,033
Tolong buat laporan operasi ini...,

239
00:20:47,403 --> 00:20:50,573
...dan memprosesnya.

240
00:20:59,252 --> 00:21:01,323
Aku tidak berniat membuatnya
mengalami hal ini.

241
