354
00:31:04,482 --> 00:31:05,922
Apa Anda tak takut?

355
00:31:06,192 --> 00:31:07,393
Permisi sebentar.

356
00:31:07,922 --> 00:31:09,222
Kondisi kalian sudah mendingan?

357
00:31:09,363 --> 00:31:11,022
Oppa!

358
00:31:11,762 --> 00:31:12,793
Oppa.

359
00:31:15,303 --> 00:31:16,863
