363
00:31:23,942 --> 00:31:25,113
Kau takkan mati hanya karena
luka di kakimu.

364
00:31:25,373 --> 00:31:26,412
Kau selamatkanlah nyawamu sendiri.

365
00:31:26,613 --> 00:31:27,742
Dia seksi sekali.

366
00:31:28,212 --> 00:31:29,813
