banyak rahasia, ya?

412
00:34:57,529 --> 00:34:58,899
Dia seperti orang yang berbeda.

413
00:34:58,999 --> 00:35:00,429
Tatapan matanya berbeda.

414
00:35:00,730 --> 00:35:02,730
